<p>Yes, there is a contradiction, and I&#8217;ve always seen Thumper as a happy-go-lucky poster who sees that conflict but won&#8217;t let it get in the way of him saying how he feels. That&#8217;s one of the ways he manages to write so well. We are all supposed to adults reading this stuff, after all. I think you&#8217;d do well to ease up on the lad.</p>
