	   				   				   		</div>
	   		
	   		<div class="col460 clear">
	       		<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/237741599c194a7328563c1f1fe1d302?s=50&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D50&amp;r=X' class='avatar avatar-50 photo' height='50' width='50' />	   				   			<p>sounds like a failure to take responsibility to me&#8230; you can&#8217;t write something like that (clearly NOT just about him) in the public domain and then say it&#8217;s got nothing to do with anyone else!</p>
